                                            long-term results.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">How long does a DIY garden path
                                            last?</h3>
                                        <p class="text-gray-700">With proper base preparation and durable materials, a
                                            garden path can last for many years. Maintenance also helps extend its life.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Conclusion</h2>
                                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                                    A DIY garden path is a simple project that adds structure, beauty, and cleanliness
